reviewText: Love! We need more Spanish Christian music like this in America <3
Had seen it before and that is why I decided to buy it! I recommend it. It combines not only songs, but also some talk, which is very nice.
Lo recomiendo, excelente el sonido, muy bien preparado todo, se escucha muy claro y visualmente es igual de tremenda calidad. De los mejores conciertos que he visto.
